        {
            "id": 6011465,
            "title": "谷歌Gemini app推出「排程計畫」功能 讓AI個人助理更主動、更強大",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Google (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>) 宣佈在其 Gemini 應用中推出一項名為「排程計畫」的新功能，旨在主動管理用戶的任務，使應用程式更加個人化、主動性和強大。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011465%2Fl%2F4de3a55e0dcd331c4d2302d67b95031d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">（圖：REUTERS/TPG）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>「排程計畫」功能可讓使用者自動執行日常任務或直接從 Gemini 接收個人化更新。使用者可以指示 Gemini 在特定時間執行任務，或將現有提示轉換為重複操作。此操作可隨時在應用程式 (app) 設定中的計劃操作頁面上進行管理。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>「排程計畫」功能提供多種應用場景。例如，用戶可以在醒來後查看日曆摘要和未讀郵件，或請 Gemini 每週一產生五個部落格創意。用戶還可以隨時關注自己喜愛的運動隊伍的最新動態，或安排一次性任務，例如要求 Gemini 在頒獎典禮結束後的第二天提供頒獎典禮的摘要。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>目前，「排程計畫」功能開放給擁有 Google AI Pro 或 Ultra 訂閱且符合 Google Workspace 商務和教育計畫資格的 Gemini app 用戶。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
